OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a cold start for many it
OL,6,Fwill be a dry day with some long
OL,7,Fspells of sunshine and fairly light
OL,8,Fbreezes, although windier for the
OL,9,FHebrides later in the day. Tending to
OL,10,Fcloud over later in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry clear evening for much
OL,13,Fof the area but rain moving across the
OL,14,FHebrides will spread east during the
OL,15,Fnight, cloudy and windy with further
OL,16,Frain by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
