OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA wet and windy start to
OL,6,FSunday, perhaps the far north dry
OL,7,Funtil mid-morning. Drier for a time in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon before further rain
OL,9,Fspreads north later in the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA wet
OL,12,Fstart to the new week but rain
OL,13,Fclearing later on Monday, some settled
OL,14,Fconditions on Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,15,Fwith some March sunshine breaking
OL,16,Fthrough.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
